1
00:00:19,162 --> 00:00:24,349
♪The whole world is lit up♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:25,661
♪Because you exist♪

3
00:00:25,662 --> 00:00:27,741
♪You're always♪

4
00:00:27,742 --> 00:00:32,391
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

5
00:00:32,392 --> 00:00:35,124
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

6
00:00:35,125 --> 00:00:36,691
♪Hold tight♪

7
00:00:36,692 --> 00:00:42,481
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

8
00:00:42,482 --> 00:00:48,145
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 23=

9
00:00:51,740 --> 00:00:52,938
Guess what I saw?

10
00:00:52,939 --> 00:00:53,938
What was it?

11
00:00:53,939 --> 00:00:55,338
He Group actually managed

12
00:00:55,339 --> 00:00:57,520
to secure the latest masterpiece
"Changing Mountains and Rivers"

13
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:58,640
by the Chinese-style artist Hong.

14
00:00:58,640 --> 00:00:59,658
They also announced

15
00:00:59,659 --> 00:01:00,978
that on the day of the auction,

16
00:01:00,979 --> 00:01:03,579
Hong will be there in person
with the masterpiece to show support.

17
00:01:03,619 --> 00:01:05,019
No way.

18
00:01:05,059 --> 00:01:07,299
Hong is showing up at their auction?

19
00:01:09,259 --> 00:01:10,860
So we have no chance of winning?

20
00:01:11,339 --> 00:01:13,939
Is this for real?
How come I haven't heard about it?

21
00:01:13,940 --> 00:01:14,379
It's true.

22
00:01:14,380 --> 00:01:15,379
Don't worry.

23
00:01:24,180 --> 00:01:25,179
Yu.

24
00:01:28,259 --> 00:01:29,340
Let's talk.

25
00:01:30,219 --> 00:01:31,739
I have nothing to talk about with you.

26
00:01:32,859 --> 00:01:33,819
Mr. He,

27
00:01:34,180 --> 00:01:35,539
just say what's on your mind.

28
00:01:35,740 --> 00:01:36,980
Shen Jibai,

29
00:01:37,180 --> 00:01:38,379
you're really an eyesore.

30
00:01:38,779 --> 00:01:40,459
All of Mu Group belongs to you now,

31
00:01:40,460 --> 00:01:42,160
yet you still want
to drag her down with you?

32
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:43,099
Mr. He,

33
00:01:43,460 --> 00:01:45,138
everything Zhiyu and I are doing

34
00:01:45,139 --> 00:01:47,620
is to protect the legacy
of her grandfather and mother.

35
00:01:47,740 --> 00:01:48,939
Is there a problem with that?

36
00:01:51,219 --> 00:01:53,179
It's a small world indeed.

37
00:01:53,180 --> 00:01:54,900
I see you two everywhere.

38
00:01:55,219 --> 00:01:57,459
Ye Li was my
defeated opponent back then.

39
00:01:57,859 --> 00:01:59,060
Today,

40
00:01:59,580 --> 00:02:01,260
you two are destined to lose too.

41
00:02:01,419 --> 00:02:03,418
Someone who was kicked out of Mu Group

42
00:02:03,419 --> 00:02:05,140
is making such bold claims here.

43
00:02:05,619 --> 00:02:07,060
You're quite amusing.

44
00:02:09,260 --> 00:02:10,179
Let's go.

45
00:02:10,180 --> 00:02:11,539
Don't waste your breath on them.

46
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:15,419
Yu,

47
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:19,180
if you're willing to give in,

48
00:02:20,140 --> 00:02:21,139
I might consider

49
00:02:21,140 --> 00:02:22,580
letting Mu Group off the hook.

50
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:29,460
Mr. He,

51
00:02:29,580 --> 00:02:31,060
at this point,

52
00:02:31,099 --> 00:02:33,659
do you still expect Mu Zhiyu
to come back and beg you?

53
00:02:33,939 --> 00:02:34,979
I heard

54
00:02:34,980 --> 00:02:36,979
they'll be getting married
after the auction.

55
00:02:36,980 --> 00:02:38,579
You should focus on

56
00:02:38,580 --> 00:02:40,658
how to make them fail miserably

57
00:02:40,659 --> 00:02:42,180
at this auction.

58
00:02:44,379 --> 00:02:45,579
You don't need

59
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:46,818
to worry about my affairs.

60
00:02:46,819 --> 00:02:49,740
But we're in the same boat now.

61
00:02:50,499 --> 00:02:52,300
I hope you can stay focused.

62
00:02:53,339 --> 00:02:54,740
I have my own plans.

63
00:02:57,212 --> 00:02:58,859
(He Group)

64
00:02:58,860 --> 00:03:01,939
Good evening, collectors and guests.

65
00:03:02,140 --> 00:03:04,220
Thank you for attending this auction.

66
00:03:04,539 --> 00:03:05,740
Next,

67
00:03:05,860 --> 00:03:08,419
we will begin bidding
for our first collection.

68
00:03:08,420 --> 00:03:10,939
This round will use
a 2-5-8 bidding increment.

69
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:14,720
(He Group, Saddle Up Two Horses)
The starting price is 10 million yuan.

70
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:17,019
Each increment will be 2 million yuan.

71
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:18,340
Please raise your paddles to bid.

72
00:03:19,460 --> 00:03:20,500
10 million.

73
00:03:22,099 --> 00:03:23,620
12 million.

74
00:03:23,779 --> 00:03:24,699
Next,

75
00:03:24,700 --> 00:03:27,379
(Gilded Bronze Phoenix Head Pot)
we begin the auction for our first item,

76
00:03:27,740 --> 00:03:29,900
the Gilded Bronze Phoenix Head Pot.

77
00:03:30,099 --> 00:03:32,459
This is a piece of metalware
from the Tang Dynasty,

78
00:03:32,460 --> 00:03:35,259
renowned for its exquisite
craftsmanship and unique shape.

79
00:03:35,420 --> 00:03:38,778
It is a representative masterpiece
of Tang gold and silverware.

80
00:03:38,779 --> 00:03:39,900
The starting price is

81
00:03:40,580 --> 00:03:41,859
20 million.

82
00:03:42,819 --> 00:03:44,300
Bidding starts now.

83
00:03:44,779 --> 00:03:47,659
(Gilded Bronze Phoenix Head Pot)
21 million.

84
00:03:47,779 --> 00:03:49,180
(Mu Group, He Group)
16 million.

85
00:03:49,260 --> 00:03:50,378
23 million.

86
00:03:50,379 --> 00:03:51,460
10 million.

87
00:03:55,740 --> 00:03:58,020
With Hong's "Changing
Mountains and Rivers" as the finale,

88
00:03:58,499 --> 00:04:00,020
we are sure to win.

89
00:04:02,420 --> 00:04:04,900
I've already had
the news leaked to Mu Group.

90
00:04:05,020 --> 00:04:07,699
Everyone wants to see Hong in person.

91
00:04:08,339 --> 00:04:09,538
The people from their side

92
00:04:09,539 --> 00:04:10,658
will all come over too.

93
00:04:10,659 --> 00:04:12,060
Well, let's wish

94
00:04:12,539 --> 00:04:13,939
that they don't lose too badly.

95
00:04:16,539 --> 00:04:19,260
23 million, last call.

96
00:04:20,539 --> 00:04:21,460
Sold!

97
00:04:21,580 --> 00:04:24,179
Congratulations to this gentleman
for successfully bidding on this item.

98
00:04:31,219 --> 00:04:32,840
(Gilded Bronze Phoenix Head Pot)
I've been waiting so long,

99
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:34,098
but I haven't seen anything good.

100
00:04:34,099 --> 00:04:35,260
I think

101
00:04:35,419 --> 00:04:37,539
we might as well
check out the place next door.

102
00:04:38,020 --> 00:04:40,460
I heard the Chinese-style artist Hong

103
00:04:40,580 --> 00:04:42,520
will be making
a grand finale appearance soon.

104
00:04:43,060 --> 00:04:44,859
Anyone want to go take a look?

105
00:04:46,099 --> 00:04:46,900
Let's go.

106
00:04:53,060 --> 00:04:53,900
Mr. He.

107
00:04:53,979 --> 00:04:54,780
Mr. He.

108
00:04:55,299 --> 00:04:56,019
Next,

109
00:04:56,020 --> 00:04:58,579
is it time for Hong's
"Changing Mountains and Rivers"

110
00:04:58,580 --> 00:04:59,979
to take center stage as the finale?

111
00:05:00,225 --> 00:05:01,025
Exactly.

112
00:05:01,380 --> 00:05:02,140
So,

113
00:05:02,659 --> 00:05:04,179
will Hong really

114
00:05:05,419 --> 00:05:06,419
show up here?

115
00:05:07,140 --> 00:05:08,419
Wait just a moment,

116
00:05:08,500 --> 00:05:10,380
and you'll get
the answer you're looking for.

117
00:05:11,140 --> 00:05:12,220
Great, great.

118
00:05:13,620 --> 00:05:15,579
I came all the way
from Mu Group's auction

119
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:17,099
just to see Hong.

120
00:05:17,620 --> 00:05:19,059
It looks like it's almost over.

121
00:05:19,060 --> 00:05:19,819
Where is he?

122
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:20,819
Mr. He,

123
00:05:20,820 --> 00:05:23,739
we've been waiting
for Hong for a long time.

124
00:05:23,940 --> 00:05:25,579
Is Hong really coming or not?

125
00:05:25,580 --> 00:05:26,739
Yeah.

126
00:05:28,020 --> 00:05:29,380
Should we check on it?

127
00:05:31,675 --> 00:05:38,019
(Moser International,
Gilded Bronze Phoenix Head Pot)

128
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:38,819
Miss Mu,

129
00:05:38,820 --> 00:05:40,020
sorry I'm late.

130
00:05:40,419 --> 00:05:43,579
Mr. Hong asked me to deliver
"Changing Mountains and Rivers" to you.

131
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:45,739
He has decided to have it
auctioned by Mu Group.

132
00:05:46,460 --> 00:05:47,619
Mr. Shen,

133
00:05:47,700 --> 00:05:48,700
Boss,

134
00:05:49,020 --> 00:05:52,419
why don't you hand it
to Miss Mu yourself?

135
00:06:07,020 --> 00:06:12,338
Alright. Mu Group is about to auction
"Changing Mountains and Rivers."

136
00:06:12,339 --> 00:06:14,819
Hong's assistant
personally delivered the painting.

137
00:06:14,820 --> 00:06:16,979
What? "Changing Mountains and Rivers"
is at Mu Group?

138
00:06:17,419 --> 00:06:18,738
I just came from there.

139
00:06:18,739 --> 00:06:19,820
Are you kidding me?

140
00:06:20,020 --> 00:06:21,139
Whatever.

141
00:06:21,140 --> 00:06:22,700
We've waited this long.

142
00:06:22,739 --> 00:06:24,098
Since He Group can't produce it,

143
00:06:24,099 --> 00:06:25,658
let's go see it at Mu Group.

144
00:06:25,659 --> 00:06:26,379
Fine, let's go.

145
00:06:26,380 --> 00:06:27,939
Let's go. Go check it out at Mu Group.

146
00:06:27,940 --> 00:06:28,619
Let's go.

147
00:06:28,700 --> 00:06:29,539
Wait for me.

148
00:06:30,260 --> 00:06:31,098
Wait for me.

149
00:06:31,099 --> 00:06:32,218
- Let's go.
- Go.

150
00:06:32,219 --> 00:06:33,260
Wait a bit more.

151
00:06:33,739 --> 00:06:34,338
Let's go.

152
00:06:34,339 --> 00:06:35,419
Just go and see.

153
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:36,379
No way.

154
00:06:36,380 --> 00:06:37,619
I have to go see for myself.

155
00:06:39,537 --> 00:06:41,382
(Mu Group)

156
00:06:44,620 --> 00:06:45,739
What are you doing up here?

157
00:06:50,179 --> 00:06:50,978
Do you think taking

158
00:06:50,979 --> 00:06:53,100
any random painting can pass
for "Changing Mountains and Rivers"?

159
00:06:55,380 --> 00:06:57,140
I brought it here myself.

160
00:06:58,380 --> 00:06:59,499
How could it be fake?

161
00:07:00,339 --> 00:07:02,298
Hong clearly agreed
to cooperate with us.

162
00:07:02,299 --> 00:07:03,979
How could he go back on his word?

163
00:07:05,299 --> 00:07:09,059
You haven't even met Mr. Hong.
When did he ever agree to work with you?

164
00:07:09,060 --> 00:07:10,140
That's impossible.

165
00:07:10,700 --> 00:07:12,460
We clearly had a deal.

166
00:07:14,500 --> 00:07:15,700
Is it you?

167
00:07:15,739 --> 00:07:18,059
Are you lying to us
on purpose for Shen Jibai?

168
00:07:19,580 --> 00:07:21,739
Since you don't believe what I'm saying,

169
00:07:21,940 --> 00:07:23,539
let Mr. Hong

170
00:07:23,779 --> 00:07:24,979
tell you himself.

171
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:32,282
(Mu Group)

172
00:07:32,299 --> 00:07:33,460
Mr. Hong.

173
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:47,539
I did indeed promise

174
00:07:47,659 --> 00:07:48,778
that I would bring my new work

175
00:07:48,779 --> 00:07:50,020
to meet everyone.

176
00:07:50,380 --> 00:07:51,419
However,

177
00:07:51,460 --> 00:07:53,179
other than Zhiyu,

178
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:58,539
there will never be a second person
who can auction my work.

179
00:08:00,940 --> 00:08:02,460
You are Mr. Hong?

180
00:08:13,099 --> 00:08:14,139
Miss Mu,

181
00:08:14,140 --> 00:08:16,739
remember I said we'd meet again
if we were destined?

182
00:08:17,580 --> 00:08:19,340
He's just a rough bodyguard.

183
00:08:19,380 --> 00:08:21,179
How could he be a Chinese-style artist?

184
00:08:22,700 --> 00:08:24,340
We've been played.

185
00:08:38,025 --> 00:08:41,720
("Changing Mountains and Rivers"
Chinese-style artist Hong's new work)

186
00:08:46,087 --> 00:08:49,782
("Changing Mountains and Rivers")

187
00:08:51,860 --> 00:08:52,940
Next,

188
00:08:53,380 --> 00:08:55,979
we will auction
the final exhibit of the day,

189
00:08:58,860 --> 00:09:00,259
"Changing Mountains and Rivers".

190
00:09:05,380 --> 00:09:06,300
Zhiyu.

191
00:09:07,539 --> 00:09:08,660
Zhiyu.

192
00:09:10,100 --> 00:09:11,180
Shen Jibai,

193
00:09:12,299 --> 00:09:14,139
you kept me in the dark for so long.

194
00:09:14,140 --> 00:09:16,019
I think you owe me an explanation.

195
00:09:16,340 --> 00:09:17,418
I just never found

196
00:09:17,419 --> 00:09:18,739
the right opportunity to tell you.

197
00:09:18,740 --> 00:09:20,619
So you just let me worry all this time?

198
00:09:21,220 --> 00:09:23,019
In fact, you had a plan all along.

199
00:09:23,619 --> 00:09:25,860
If you're going to put on a show,
you have to go all the way.

200
00:09:25,900 --> 00:09:26,899
To deal with enemies,

201
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:28,818
you have to wait
until they are at their most smug

202
00:09:28,819 --> 00:09:30,300
to deal the fatal blow.

203
00:09:36,539 --> 00:09:38,619
You knew how much
I hate feeling out of control,

204
00:09:38,659 --> 00:09:40,019
yet you still treated me like this,

205
00:09:40,699 --> 00:09:42,340
lying to me over and over again.

206
00:09:44,419 --> 00:09:45,300
Tell me,

207
00:09:45,579 --> 00:09:47,259
what else are you hiding from me?

208
00:09:51,459 --> 00:09:52,420
There is one thing.

209
00:10:00,619 --> 00:10:02,660
And that is that I really want
to hold you right now.

210
00:10:04,419 --> 00:10:05,779
I promise you,

211
00:10:07,059 --> 00:10:09,460
I will never hide
anything from you again.

212
00:10:10,299 --> 00:10:12,099
I'll tell you everything.

213
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:19,320
Don't think that just
because you're doing this,

214
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,540
I'll forgive you.

215
00:10:26,980 --> 00:10:28,779
Then, I'll apologize properly tonight.

216
00:10:31,340 --> 00:10:34,060
An apology isn't just something you say.

217
00:10:34,900 --> 00:10:36,139
I'll see how sincere you are.

218
00:10:38,140 --> 00:10:39,580
Slow down.

219
00:10:46,340 --> 00:10:47,060
Okay.

220
00:10:47,459 --> 00:10:48,259
Sit down.

221
00:10:53,380 --> 00:10:55,779
I've also prepared
a surprise for you tonight.

222
00:10:57,939 --> 00:10:59,619
In front of you,

223
00:11:00,380 --> 00:11:02,460
there are three special drinks.

224
00:11:03,699 --> 00:11:05,099
Pick one and drink it,

225
00:11:05,299 --> 00:11:06,619
and I'll forgive you.

226
00:11:14,220 --> 00:11:15,219
From the smell of it,

227
00:11:15,220 --> 00:11:16,499
something doesn't seem right.

228
00:11:16,719 --> 00:11:18,019
Are you going to drink it or not?

229
00:11:19,140 --> 00:11:20,019
I'll drink it.

230
00:11:20,539 --> 00:11:23,019
As long as you're the one who made it,
I'd even drink poison.

231
00:11:44,579 --> 00:11:46,180
How much salt did you put in this?

232
00:11:46,539 --> 00:11:48,820
Do you want to use
the other two to rinse your mouth?

233
00:11:52,299 --> 00:11:53,700
I'll let you have a taste too.

234
00:12:02,579 --> 00:12:03,940
Not here.

235
00:12:53,179 --> 00:12:56,178
Ms. Xu, your assistant, Zhao Ye, has been
taken by the police for investigation

236
00:12:56,179 --> 00:12:57,820
on suspicion of intentional injury.

237
00:12:57,900 --> 00:12:59,480
The police
have already entered the group

238
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:01,300
and are preparing
for an in-depth investigation.

239
00:13:09,539 --> 00:13:12,139
Shen Jibai, Mu Zhiyu...

240
00:13:13,579 --> 00:13:15,979
Since you want
to drive me into a corner,

241
00:13:16,900 --> 00:13:19,060
don't blame me for being ruthless.

242
00:13:20,740 --> 00:13:21,859
What do you plan to do?

243
00:13:30,275 --> 00:13:34,505
♪Light comes beaming in♪

244
00:13:34,645 --> 00:13:39,014
♪Landing on my skin♪

245
00:13:39,015 --> 00:13:43,505
♪Warms the space you left behind♪

246
00:13:47,725 --> 00:13:51,664
♪Shadows move around♪

247
00:13:51,665 --> 00:13:56,274
♪Awake, racing thoughts♪

248
00:13:56,275 --> 00:14:00,805
♪Try to keep the memories safe♪

249
00:14:04,405 --> 00:14:10,195
♪Don't slip away♪

250
00:14:12,645 --> 00:14:17,214
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

251
00:14:17,215 --> 00:14:21,614
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

252
00:14:21,615 --> 00:14:25,935
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

253
00:14:25,955 --> 00:14:29,935
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

254
00:14:30,405 --> 00:14:34,714
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

255
00:14:34,715 --> 00:14:39,044
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

256
00:14:39,045 --> 00:14:43,354
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

257
00:14:43,355 --> 00:14:49,505
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪
